But anyway from my own experience you can get more outta bind wound than sitting if you time yourself with game ticks, maybe he forgot that, maybe my tests were wrong, will redo tests and log to have numbers, it's not that much, but it's faster.<br>
<br>
About the code comment, you forget that they also cut stuff to free ressources. They stopped pet doing their little patrol not cuz mage were asking for it, it didn't make people sea sick, but because it frees ressources for other usage. The code behind a game like this has to stay as simple as possible, cause every little flaw is cascaded by 1000s of users. Every single thing does count, cause once you start makin exception, then you make others, and soon there isn't just 1 more operation, there's 5 wich used by 1000 users mean 5000 instead of 1000. They have good servers, but ressources are not infinite, they can't watch every damn thing hehe. <br>
<br>
Bind wound is not class defining for mage, considered all my life i was summoning them for others (they bind better than me anyway), I gave them to people in group so they could heal while I med. I dòn't think it's worth more CPU time. If you want better bind wound, ask for skill increase, much better solution imho.<br>
