<br>
I read all these Damage Per Second reports and it's disheartening.<br>
<br>
With such a lack in defense, wouldn't you expect an increase in offense?  In terms of killing power &amp; efficiency, a pure damage-dealing caster should offer more than any melee; the tradeoff being that you cannot survive much damage at all, and you need your melee friends to protect you.  Wizard should more than equal a Rogue.  Mage + pet should equal a Wizard.<br>
