The whole 6-mages with a special aa summoning an uber pet of doom would indeed be very awesome, and wouldnt seem to unbalance the class because it would indeed be hard to find the 6 mages required to summon this beast. When I started the game I imagined our pets (because they were hardly referred to as pets in that intro manual) as being creatures of great power and magnificent form, not floating blobs of whatever element...<br>
