<br>
Now that I can totally agree with - though I disagree that a warrior does not require a cleric.  They may have high regen, but they get utterly ripped by the mobs they're fighting at that stage.  Grouping with a Shaman is a wise move for them - but that applies to any of us.  Slow + Haste works just dandy, and at that point the heals needed really aren't of cleric level.<br>
<br>
And yes, I'm aware that monks can evade/dodge quite well - but it's not until they have massive resists that they can avoid the spellcasting that seems prevalent among just about every mob post-58.  His/her hps aren't all that much higher than mine, and since he/she doesn't have a pocket tank to throw at the mob, the monk had better be able to avoid damage...<br>
<br>
But all this hardly makes me a non-solo-capable character - and that rogue who just hit &quot;a&quot; better not whine when my pet dishes him out of his xps.  <br>
